    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the prawns have started to turn pink, add the <strong>cooked Thai rice noodles</strong>, <strong>coconut stock</strong> and <strong>mangetout</strong> to the pan</p><p>Wash the <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with <strong>kitchen paper</strong></p><p>Stir through the<strong> spinach </strong>and cook for 2 min until the spinach has wilted and the mangetout has started to soften – this is your <strong>Thai green prawn noodle soup</strong></p>",
